            <Title>Physical Book</Title>
            <Text>PHYSICAL BOOK A companion book that, providing the project is popular and makes some money, will be published by Transworld and distributed to sit alongside the main piece. Features Not A Novel This is not a tie-in book. It will contain a separate story, tied in with “making-of” sections of the main experience, links back to web content, art and commentary, and be all-in-all a “connected manuscript” - available as a ebook and physical book, with deep hooks embedded that lead back to the ocean of the web.</Text>
